org.sbml.jsbml.ontology

Class Triple

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sbml.jsbml.ontology.Triple
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<Triple>

    public class Triple
extends Object
implements Cloneable, Comparable<Triple>, Serializable
    This is a wrapper class for the corresponding BioJava class Triple, to allow for simplified access to the properties of a subject-predicate-object triple in this ontology.
